ounty+Register&amp;rft.atitle=Nixon+library+director+leaves+mixed+legacy&amp;rft.date=2011-11-17&amp;rft.au=Whiting%2C+David&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ocregister.com%2Farticles%2Fnaftali-327486-nixon-watergate.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ATimothy+Naftali\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Naftali, Tim. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cnn.com/2017/03/23/opinions/being-donald-trump-naftali-opinion/index.html\">\"Being Donald Trump: a president living in his own fantasy world\"</a>. <i>CNN</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2017-07-11</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=CNN&amp;rft.atitle=Being+Donald+Trump%3A+a+president+living+in+his+own+fantasy+world&amp;rft.aulast=Naftali&amp;rft.aufirst=Tim&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2017%2F03%2F23%2Fopinions%2Fbeing-donald-trump-naftali-opinion%2Findex.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ATimothy+Naftali\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-goldberg-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-goldberg_6-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Goldberg, Jeffrey (May 8, 2007). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.jeffreygoldberg.net/articles/tny/the_talk_of_the_town_sprucing.php\">\"The Talk of the Town: Sprucing Up Nixon\"</a>. <i>The New Yorker</i>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+New+Yorker&amp;rft.atitle=The+Talk+of+the+Town%3A+Sprucing+Up+Nixon&amp;rft.d